rComments: She is enthusiastic about what she is teaching, which what I loved most about this course. She is clear with the subject matter. I truly enjoyed this class.

Interesting class but VERY challenging. Pretty difficult to get an "A" on anything. Very knowledgeable in her field but seems to let her personal views toward artists/works factor into grades. NOT a blow-off class.
Excellent Professor!  Her lectures were diligently prepared and always brilliant.  No matter your level of knowledge of art I would recommend a class with Prof. Small.  One of the best on campus!
